。「切勿逕送上級法院」\r\n                              書記官  楊茗瑋\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　1 　　月　　26　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TTDM/111%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c5%2c20220125%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TTDM,111,單禁沒,5,20220125,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"5","JDATE":"20220125","JTITLE":"宣告沒收"}